      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, which arrives in an impeccable state of preservation. This vehicle reflects an uncompromising standard of care, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a curated interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and mechanically peerless, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning driver to acquire a vehicle of distinguished provenance and absolute integrity.",
